	   <a name=98595807669272></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98595807669272><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=13&mid=98595807669272>Armor Class is the most important</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=13&mid=98595807669272#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
