	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98589815553118><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=13&mid=98589815553118>RE: IS INTELIGENCE really more Important to an enchie than C</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=13&mid=98589815553118#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
