	   <tr><td colspan=2>im a lvl 12 chanter. in all my live, i had found only 2 people who understand how does mezmerize work. They now are my best friends ;)<br> When im not with them, and i found a new group, if i had time, i teach what mezz does: pull a green-@#%^y mob, attack, and mez. After I run near him, jump, make some rude postures and after i sit in front of him.<br> If i dont have the time to teach this, i only say that dont use AE spells, and use assist on the main tank. If your group does that, you are relatively safe. The only problem is if mezz dont work, the mob agro you. Try to use mezz and after mem blur. It saved my life sometimes.<br> And if you say all that and they still use AE, or dont use assist, find a better group.<br><br>Massagran- lvl 12 chanter<br>solusek ro server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
