	   <tr><td colspan=2>Thicken mana, and all the spells in this line are going to be used in tailoring skills to make magic armour. Most recently (3-15-01) there was the addition of a erudite cultrue armour that all need a vial of distilled mana or other "tangable mana" as I call it. The spells can only be found in a brownie camp in the NW corner of lower faydark and you need to have illusion earth elemental or wolf form cast upon you from another player (i havent tried the latter). The reagents are usually a poision vial and a pearl. see www.castersrealm.com for details. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
