	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've heard many complaints lately that characters in Blackburrow gain a level, then die right away and lose the level again.&nbsp;&nbsp;Here's my way of preventing that.  Keep a stack of gnoll fangs.  As soon as you level up, go to South Qeynos and turn in the gnoll fangs, and then the moonstones.  You should now have an experience buffer for fighting in Blackburrow.<br>Hope it helps.<br>&nbsp;<br>Druid Bolooen Naturewolf :-)<br>Morrell-Thule<br></td></tr>
